The perspective is from a low angle, looking upwards towards the sky, giving a sense of scale and grandeur to the scene. Cars and buses are parked along the side of the road, hinting at the busy traffic typical of city life. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The sky itself is a clear blue, with the sun shining brightly, casting shadows and highlighting the architectural details of the buildings.
